posts.post_title: WTB or trade for HOFers with rare backs
posts.post_content: Looking for HOFers with Hindu and rarer backs.  Have cash or a ton of cards to trade.  Probably have 100 or 150 mid-tier backs that could be used in trade.  Or have cash.  This group is like 90% trade bait only.  Only a few I'd sell.

Random Little Rascal Kid – Remarkable.
Spanky – Isn't there another word you know ??

Spanky – Well, for the love of Pete, say it !!!
